/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"执行每日 skill 升级检查。\\n\\n1. 运行 `clawhub list` 查看当前已装的 skill\\n2. 运行 `clawhub update --all --no-input --force` 升级所有 skill\\n3. 如果有 skill 升级失败，记下错误信息\\n4. 汇报格式：\\n   - 检查时间（Asia/Shanghai）\\n   - 升级成功的 skill（列出版本号变化）\\n   - 升级失败的 skill（列出错误）\\n   - 已是最新、没动的 skill（仅列数量）\\n5. 如果所有 skill 都已是最新，回复一句话即可，不要冗长\\n\\n注意：\\n- 不要主动修改配置文件\\n- 任何破坏性操作前先 stop 并汇报\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"to\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780603200000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780516800014,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 265899,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 1,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0,\n        \"lastError\": \"FallbackSummaryError: All models failed (3): minimax(49套餐)/MiniMax-M3: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"error\\\",\\\"error\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"overloaded_error\\\",\\\"message\\\":\\\"server is busy, please retry later\\\"}} (overloaded) | minimax/MiniMax-M2.7: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"error\\\",\\\"error\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"overloaded_error\\\",\\\"message\\\":\\\"server is busy, please retry later\\\"}} (overloaded) | openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash:free: 401 User not found. (auth)\",\n        \"lastDiagnostics\": {\n          \"summary\": \"All models failed (3): minimax(49套餐)/MiniMax-M3: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"error\\\",\\\"error\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"overloaded_error\\\",\\\"message\\\":\\\"server is busy, please retry later\\\"}} (overloaded) | minimax/MiniMax-M2.7: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"error\\\",\\\"error\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"overloaded_error\\\",\\\"message\\\":\\\"server is busy, pl