ng \\\"写进去呀\\\" - they want me to actually write all the data. Let me do this properly now - I'll update each of the 3 records with all the remaining fields.\\n\\nI need to update the 3 records I created:\\n- Record 1 (recvltZIbjniKh): S级 发带, 月销25902, $1.84, ¥0.78, 51%, 越南, 推荐等级S, 采集状态已采\\n\\n, 行动建议立即采购50-100件\\n- Record 2: A级 发夹, 月销22254, $1.53, ¥0.78, 48%, 越南, 推荐等级A, 采集状态已采集, 行动建议正常采购30-50件\\n- Record 3: A级 发爪夹, 月销5053, $2.03, ¥1.2, 53%, 越南, 推荐等级A, 采集状态已采集, 行动建议正常采购30-50件\\n\\nLet me update all 3 records with the complete data now.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"6d34145819cede6f10193a9e69cd25222d9fb7ccbb9af4c57b29e4bc039f7519\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\n好，马上写！刚才成功写入了基础数据，现在把完整字段都补进去。一次5个字段以内，分批写：\\n\\n**第一条（S级发带）更新完整字段：**\\n\\napp_token = `AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd`\\ntable_id = `tblHU2do30jzinJT`\\nrecord_id = `recvltZIbjniKh`\\n\\n| 等级 | 商品 | 月销 | 售价 | 毛利 |\\n|----"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":47,"aggregated":"{\"type\":\"custom_message\",\"customType\":\"openclaw.runtime-context\",\"content\":\"System: [2026-06-03 20:28:58 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b6d35ae535cb4c499bc11ac67af3]\",\"display\":false,\"details\":{\"source\":\"openclaw-runtime-context\"},\"id\":\"8f76f584\",\"parentId\":\"f86cc748\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-03T12:29:06.188Z\"}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"887842c5\",\"parentId\":\"8f76f584\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-03T12:29:24.719Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"The user is saying \\\"写进去呀\\\" (write it in/to the table!). They want me to actually write the records into the Feishu bitable. \\n\\nI've been trying to write records but they were failing with NOTEXIST. Then I found that writing with minimal fields worked. But I also need to write the remaining fields for the records (not just the first record with minimal fields).\\n\\nLooking at what happened:\\n1. First I wrote record 1 with just 商品名称 and 月销