US 双站 + 1688货源（`tiktok_category_report` VN接口仍无数据，改用 `tiktok_similar_product` 搜索词替代）\\n- **VN站爆款：** Kẹp Tết Tóc Mái 3 Tầng（月销44,429，棋盘格韩式发夹爆款）\\n- **US站爆款：** Checkerboard Pattern Hair Claws（周销量从62暴增至3452，爆款飙升）\\n- **飞书写入：** 需要确认权限——之前多维表写入曾报 `1254302` 权限错误，需要你在多维表里添加 bot 编辑权限\\n\\n报告里包含 10 个 VN 候选品 + 3 个 US 候选品 + 5 个 1688 货源，按 SOP 筛选了增长率和评分。\\n\\n**等你确认：需要我写入飞书多维表吗？如果需要，先确认 bot 权限已经加上（多维表 → 分享 → 添加 TK选品大师 可编辑权限）。**\",\n      \"runAtMs\": 1779238800025,\n      \"durationMs\": 806342,\n      \"nextRunAtMs\": 1779325200000,\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n      \"usage\": {\n        \"input_tokens\": 119092,\n        \"output_tokens\": 16993,\n        \"total_tokens\": 118243\n      },\n      \"delivered\": true,\n      \"deliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"intended\": {\n          \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n          \"to\": null,\n          \"accountId\": \"tts\",\n          \"source\": \"explicit\"\n        },\n        \"resolved\": {\n          \"ok\": true,\n          \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n          \"to\": \"user:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n          \"accountId\": \"tts\",\n          \"source\": \"last\"\n        },\n        \"messageToolSentTo\": [\n          {\n            \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n            \"to\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n          }\n        ],\n        \"fallbackUsed\": false,\n        \"delivered\": true\n      },\n      \"sessionId\": \"d58952ed-eddf-418b-924c-3a6945b20f6d\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:tts:cron:5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6:run:d58952ed-eddf-418b-924c-3a6945b20f6d\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"ts\": 1779153661344,\n      \"jobId\": \"5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6\",\n      \"action\": \"finished\",\n      \"status\": \"ok\",\n      \"summary\": \"已完成今日选品流程。\\n\\n**执行摘要：**\\n- ✅ 成功调用 Sorftime API 获取 Amazon US Hair Claws 类目 Top100 数据\\n- ✅ 按 SOP 筛选（月销量≥1000、评分≥4.0、毛利率≥8%）选出 Top10\\n- ✅ 10条记录已写入飞书多维表（采集状态：待审批，选品来源：Sorftime-亚马逊数据）\\n- ✅ 选品报告已发送飞书通知\\n\\n**说明：** 本次实际执行的是**亚马逊轨道**（轨道2），因为 VN 站 TikTok 类目 API 仍返回错误。毛利率整体偏低（8-14%），因为 Amazon Hair Claws 类目以低价发夹为主（$7.99-$9.99），这是该品类的真实市场情况——低价红海竞争激烈，高端差异化产品仍有空间。\\n\\n查看表格：https://bytedance.feishu.cn/base/AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\",\n      \"runAtMs\": 1779152400006,\n      \"durationMs\": 1261298,\n      \"nextRunAtMs\": 1779238800000,\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n      \"usage\": {\n        \"input_tokens\": 97325,\n        \"output_tokens\": 33603,\n        \"total_tokens\": 95861\n      },\n      \"delivered\": true,\n      \"deliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"intended\": {\n          \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n          \"to\": null,\n          \"accountId\": \"tts\",\n          \"source\": \"explicit\"\n        },\n        \"resolved\": {\n          \"ok\": true,\n          \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n          \"to\": \"user:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n          \"accountId\": \"tts\",\n          \"source\": \"last\"\n        },\n        \"messageToolSentTo\": [\n          {\n            \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n            \"to\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n          }\n        ],\n        \"fallbackUsed\": false,\n        \"delivered\": true\n      },\n      \"sessionId\": \"b2ea6538-4712-4fa6-8fa4-b902ae2a3c4b\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:tts:cron:5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6:run:b2ea6538-4712-4fa6-8fa4-b902ae2a3c4b\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 24,\n  \"offset\": 0,\n  \"limit\": 50,\n  \"hasMore\": false,\n  \"nextOffset\": null\n}[... 12315 more characters truncated]"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["entries","total","offset","limit","hasMore","nextOffset"],"total":24},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780575543411}}
