{"type":"message","id":"fe670d3d","parentId":"913d9fe6","timestamp":"2026-06-04T12:48:15.881Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，第 81 行是 `\"streaming\": true`。我现在意识到：之前 config-validated 返回 161K 字符被截断，但是是 streaming 控制的——但是等等，让我重新看下用户说的\"小钢琴\"是什么。\n\n飞书的\"小钢琴\"通常是消息的**编辑状态指示**——当 AI 还在处理时，OpenClaw 会通过 `message` tool 持续更新同一条消息（streaming card），看起来就像消息在一直变化（图标变动像钢琴键在按动）。所以 `streaming: true` 确实是这个行为。\n\n现在我有两个选项：\n1. **直接改文件**：把 `\"streaming\": true` 改成 `\"streaming\": false`，但这会触发 hash 不匹配\n2. **用 config.apply 配合 baseHash**：完整重写配置\n\n先试直接改文件，然后让 gateway 重启加载。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1hty563moxrz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json\necho \"---\"\n# 备份\ncp /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak-2026-06-04\nls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json*"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":297,"output":271,"cacheRead":120190,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120758,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780577285394,"responseId":"0670a70577f859a355b1b2d93fee30eb"}}
