{"type":"message","id":"8a93dcd8","parentId":"9d75e930","timestamp":"2026-06-04T12:48:24.723Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"备份好了。我看到 `openclaw.json.last-good` 是 6/4 20:19 — 时间戳是今天，说明文件最近有动过。这可能是有人（包括 OpenClaw 自己）刚改过 streaming=true。让我看看上次改这个的 audit log："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_smbpu20053yn_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"tail -30 /home/halei/.openclaw/logs/config-audit.jsonl 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json\nfor line in sys.stdin:\n    try:\n        d = json.loads(line)\n        # 找 streaming 相关\n        if 'streaming' in str(d).lower() or 'feishu' in str(d).lower():\n            print(json.dumps(d, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)[:500])\n            print('---')\n    except: pass\n\" 2>&1 | head -40\necho \"===\"\n# 也直接看 audit\ntail -5 /home/halei/.openclaw/logs/config-audit.jsonl 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":444,"output":232,"cacheRead":120744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121420,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780577296241,"responseId":"0670a7107d73e61ed4242faca5e9514c"}}
