{"type":"message","id":"928da274","parentId":"bdaab717","timestamp":"2026-06-04T13:05:08.302Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到。两个问题分开处理：\n1. **表情**（小钢琴的\"键\"动画）— 关掉\n2. **流式输出**（消息一边生成一边出现的效果）— 保留\n\n之前我把整个 `streaming` 关了。问题是要保留流式但去掉状态反应表情。\n\n从之前的 schema 探查我知道：\n- `messages.statusReactions.enabled` 是控制生命周期 emoji 切换的（thinking → tool → done 这种）\n- 之前 `openclaw config set` 走 CLI 能改\n- 表情/钢琴键应该就是这个字段\n\n我先用 CLI 试关这个，验证假设。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3yiilc4ijaly_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace\n# 先看当前值（如果存在）\ngrep -A2 \"statusReactions\" /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json | head -5\necho \"---set---\"\nopenclaw config set messages.statusReactions.enabled false 2>&1 | tail -8\necho \"---verify---\"\ngrep -B1 -A3 \"statusReactions\" /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":3683,"output":259,"cacheRead":124658,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128600,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780578293237,"responseId":"0670aaf6f45b47550a822f9c118f7153"}}
