{"type":"message","id":"8aeee074","parentId":"adcc5edd","timestamp":"2026-06-04T13:05:27.552Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"CLI 改成功了，配置写在文件里了。但 CLI 提示要重启 — 不过从 schema 看 `messages.statusReactions` 的 reloadKind 是 **\"none\"**（不是 hot），所以确实需要重启。\n\n问题：刚才那次重启是 SIGUSR1，但用户说**表情还在**——意思是上一次重启完表情没消失。让我先想一下：\n\n刚才我只改了 `streaming: true → false`，**没改 statusReactions**。所以\"小钢琴\"如果指的是表情，那就是 statusReactions 的事。\n\n但用户原话是\"每次我发完消息你都回复一个小钢琴\"——这可能既包括表情也包括流式效果。不过用户说**\"还是会先回复我一条表情，小钢琴\"** — 明确是表情在前、流式在后，所以表情和流式确实可以分开。\n\n那现在问题是：刚才重启了 `streaming=false`，**流式也关了**。这跟用户说的\"不要关流式输出\"矛盾。\n\n让我重开 streaming："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9emzqdfhncwr_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace\n# 把 streaming 重新开回来\nopenclaw config set channels.feishu.streaming true 2>&1 | tail -5\necho \"---verify both---\"\ngrep -A1 \"streaming\" /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json | head -3\necho \"---\"\ngrep -B1 -A3 \"statusReactions\" /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json | head -8"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":218,"output":330,"cacheRead":128586,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129134,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780578313304,"responseId":"0670ab092fc2f3eba631ada80c39b176"}}
