{"type":"message","id":"3e922790","parentId":"f4e17947","timestamp":"2026-06-04T13:07:28.895Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到。HALEI 说\"我说是是，尽快找到原因\"——他在催我尽快找到 tts cron 失败的真实原因。\n\n让我系统地查一下。问题：**手动对话能跑通，cron 跑挂**。我之前判断\"同模型同 API 同时间窗口，只是过载撞上\"，但这个解释有点敷衍。让我把数据真的挖一遍。\n\n我需要查清楚：\n1. **手动 DM 用的什么 provider/apiKey**（authProfileOverride 写的是 `minimax:cn`，但实际跑出来 `provider: minimax` —— 那到底是哪个 apiKey 用了？）\n2. **cron isolated session 用的什么 provider/apiKey**\n3. **两个是不是真的同一个 minimax 账户**\n\n`openclaw config get` 可能能拿到 apiKey 元数据。或者我可以看 models.json 里 minimax 和 minimax-cn 的 apiKey 是不是真的一样（虽然 baseUrl 一样）。\n\n另一个角度：看请求大小、payload 长度是不是有差异（minimax 在大 payload 上挂）。手动对话的 prompt 比 cron 的 prompt 短很多。\n\n或者：minimax 的限流机制——按 accountId 或者按 sessionId 限流，cron 每次新 session 走新 ID，可能命中低优先级。\n\n让我先精确定位实际跑的 provider 和 apiKey。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wxrg49xif6yw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 1. 看 models.json 里两个 provider 的差异\ncat /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/agent/models.json 2>/dev/null\necho \"===\"\n# 2. 看 config 里 minimax 的所有 provider 配置\npython3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json') as f:\n    d = json.load(f)\nmodels = d.get('models', {}).get('providers', {})\nfor name, p in models.items():\n    if 'minimax' in name.lower() or 'minimax' in str(p.get('baseUrl', '')).lower():\n        print(f'=== {name} ===')\n        print(f'  baseUrl: {p.get(\\\"baseUrl\\\")}')\n        print(f'  apiKey: {p.get(\\\"apiKey\\\", \\\"\\\")[:25]}...')\n        print(f'  api: {p.get(\\\"api\\\")}')\n\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wxrg49xif6yw_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 2. 看 tts main session 的 model-snapshot 实际跑了什么\ntail -200 /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/sessions/54bda727-a58d-40cb-b43e-61aeda58c68d.jsonl | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\nsnapshots = []\nfor line in sys.stdin:\n    try:\n        d = json.loads(line)\n        if d.get('type') == 'custom' and d.get('customType') == 'model-snapshot':\n            snapshots.append(d['data'])\n    except: pass\nprint(f'找到 {len(snapshots)} 个 model-snapshot 记录')\nfor s in snapshots[-5:]:\n    print(f'  ts={s.get(\\\"timestamp\\\")}, provider={s.get(\\\"provider\\\")}, model={s.get(\\\"modelId\\\")}, api={s.get(\\\"modelApi\\\")}')\n\"\necho \"===\"\n# 3. cron 6/3 21:00 失败 session\ntail -200 /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/sessions/7c20fb23-5b77-4f06-ad29-698f07afdbc3.jsonl | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\nfor line in sys.stdin:\n    try:\n        d = json.loads(line)\n        if d.get('type') == 'custom' and d.get('customType') == 'model-snapshot':\n            s = d['data']\n            print(f'  ts={s.get(\\\"timestamp\\\")}, provider={s.get(\\\"provider\\\")}, model={s.get(\\\"modelId\\\")}, api={s.get(\\\"modelApi\\\")}')\n    except: pass\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":130141,"output":891,"cacheRead":114,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131146,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780578415351,"responseId":"0670ab702bd4337403153c541f2ba509"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a5c23e6a","parentId":"3e922790","timestamp":"2026-06-04T13:07:29.199Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_wxrg49xif6yw_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"providers\": {\n    \"minimax\": {\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic/v1\",\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"authHeader\": true,\n      \"models\": [\n        {\n          \"id\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"name\": \"MiniMax M2.7\",\n          \"contextWindow\": 204000,\n          \"input\": [\n            \"text\",\n            \"image\"\n          ],\n          \"reasoning\": true\n        }\n      ],\n      \"apiKey\": \"sk-cp-…s38c\"\n    },\n    \"minimax-cn\": {\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic/v1\",\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"authHeader\": true,\n      \"models\": [\n        {\n          \"id\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"name\": \"MiniMax M2.7\",\n          \"contextWindow\": 204000,\n          \"input\": [\n            \"text\",\n            \"image\"\n          ],\n          \"reasoning\": true\n        }\n      ],\n      \"apiKey\": \"sk-cp-…s38c\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n===\n=== minimax ===\n  baseUrl: https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic/v1\n  apiKey: sk-cp-…M0xB...\n  api: anthropic-messages\n=== minimax(49套餐) ===\n  baseUrl: https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic/v1\n  apiKey: sk-cp-…4q-K...\n  api: anthropic-messages"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":62,"aggregated":"{\n  \"providers\": {\n    \"minimax\": {\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic/v1\",\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"authHeader\": true,\n      \"models\": [\n        {\n          \"id\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"name\": \"MiniMax M2.7\",\n          \"contextWindow\": 204000,\n          \"input\": [\n            \"text\",\n            \"image\"\n          ],\n          \"reasoning\": true\n        }\n      ],\n      \"apiKey\": \"***\"\n    },\n    \"minimax-cn\": {\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic/v1\",\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"authHeader\": true,\n      \"models\": [\n        {\n          \"id\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"name\": \"MiniMax M2.7\",\n          \"contextWindow\": 204000,\n          \"input\": [\n            \"text\",\n            \"image\"\n          ],\n          \"reasoning\": true\n        }\n      ],\n      \"apiKey\": \"***\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n===\n=== minimax ===\n  baseUrl: https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic/v1\n  apiKey: sk-cp-…M0xB...\n  api: anthropic-messages\n=== minimax(49套餐) ===\n  baseUrl: https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic/v1\n  apiKey: sk-cp-…4q-K...\n  api: anthropic-messages","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780578449197}}
