{"type":"message","id":"77d13e64","parentId":"a8535027","timestamp":"2026-06-04T14:50:45.015Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"重要发现！**openclaw.json 里没有独立的 \"gemini\" provider**。gemini 是**通过 openrouter 访问的**（`openrouter/google/gemini-2.0-flash`）。\n\ntts agent 的 auth-profiles.json 里有个 `gemini:default` profile，apiKey 写死成 `AIzaSy…ZK7Y`，但 openclaw.json 里**没把这个 key 用上**——它指向不存在的 provider \"gemini\"。\n\n而 tts config.json 里写 `model: \"gemini/gemini-2.0-flash\"`，是希望直接调 Google Gemini API（绕过 openrouter），但实际没生效，因为顶层 provider 里没 \"gemini\"。\n\n**所以 HALEI 的怀疑是对的** — gemini 实际上不可用（要么 key 失效，要么 API 路径走不通）。\n\n我直接 ping 一下 gemini 看返回什么："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_czch78ax4vje_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 直接测 gemini API\nAPI_KEY=***\necho \"===test 1: generateContent===\"\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models/gemini-2.0-flash:generateContent?key=***\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"contents\":[{\"parts\":[{\"text\":\"ping\"}]}]}' \\\n  --max-time 15 | head -c 500\necho \"\"\necho \"===test 2: models list===\"\ncurl -s \"https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models?key=***\" --max-time 10 | head -c 500"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":193,"output":384,"cacheRead":131698,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132275,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780584632769,"responseId":"0670c3b9456e9a96192d51619e9afe50"}}
