{"type":"message","id":"8fe44852","parentId":"8f7d0105","timestamp":"2026-06-04T14:52:36.459Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"HALEI 说他给选品（tts）配置了备用模型为 3.0。\n\n我需要确认一下：\n1. 他做了什么改动？\n2. 是改的 openclaw.json 还是 tts agent config？\n3. 配置生效了吗？\n\n让我查一下当前状态。","thinkingSignature":"38dd605d9ffab73ed571f42dbd6ed60015d56e2fb8ffdf1c8bd7707fe0f30cd0"},{"type":"text","text":"收到。我先确认一下现在的配置状态："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1q5q5kq0jo65_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json') as f:\n    d = json.load(f)\n# 看 tts agent\nfor a in d.get('agents', {}).get('list', []):\n    if a.get('id') == 'tts':\n        print('=== tts agent ===')\n        print(json.dumps(a.get('model', {}), indent=2, ensure_ascii=False))\nEOF\necho \"===\"\n# tts 自己的 config\ncat /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/agent/config.json 2>/dev/null\necho \"===\"\n# 最近的 config 改动 audit\ntail -5 /home/halei/.openclaw/logs/config-audit.jsonl 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json\nfor line in sys.stdin:\n    try:\n        d = json.loads(line)\n        argv = d.get('argv', [])\n        if 'set' in argv:\n            print(f'{d.get(\\\"ts\\\", \\\"\\\")[:19]} {\\\" \\\".join(argv[argv.index(\\\"set\\\")+1:argv.index(\\\"set\\\")+3]) if \\\"set\\\" in argv else \\\"\\\"}')\"\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":132305,"output":361,"cacheRead":114,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132780,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780584741301,"responseId":"0670c4258783752de4593e48b4bb503a"}}
