{"type":"message","id":"f38b0b09","parentId":"57d00c20","timestamp":"2026-06-04T14:53:36.872Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"最近的 audit 没看到 tts model 改动（最新的是 14:47 装 lark 插件）。但 openclaw.json 里 tts model 字段确实有 fallbacks 了 — 可能是之前漏看的、或者 doctor --fix 帮修了、或者 tts config 直接被改了。\n\n无论如何，**当前 tts 的实际配置**是：\n- primary: `minimax/MiniMax-M2.7`\n- fallbacks: `[\"minimax(49套餐)/MiniMax-M3\"]`\n\n这是 HALEI 说\"备用模型为3.0\"的体现。\n\n但有个问题：**gemini 已经被踢出 fallback 链了**。HALEI 之前怀疑 gemini 不可用，但 fallback 链里其实没 gemini 什么事（gemini 只在 tts config.json 里写了一下，顶层 agents.list 里从来没用过）。\n\n不过 tts config.json 里 model 字段还写着 `gemini/gemini-2.0-flash`，但这个文件**可能不被顶层 agents.list 覆盖**？让我快速验证 — 看 tts agent 实际跑的是什么。\n\n更关键的问题：**HALEI 说他\"配置了备用模型为3.0\"** — 是要确认我吗？我应该简短确认 + 报告当前状态 + 解释下他做的事。\n\n我的回答：\n1. 确认看到了配置：tts 现在 primary = minimax/M2.7, fallback = minimax(49套餐)/M3\n2. 解释下\"独立 key\"对 fallback 的意义\n3. 问下他是否要立刻 trigger 一次 cron 验证 fallback 是否能接住\n\n等等，让我再仔细想想。HALEI 的话：\"我给选品配置了备用模型为3.0\" — 这说明他**主动改了配置**，可能用的是 commands 工具或者直接改文件。我没看到他调用工具的记录（因为是他自己改的，不是通过我）。\n\n但 audit log 里没看到 tts model 的 set 记录，说明**他可能没走 CLI**，可能：\n- 直接编辑了 openclaw.json 文件\n- 通过飞书/别的工具改的\n- 或者 doctor --fix 帮他加了\n\n无论如何，**结果是 tts 现在有 fallback 了**。这正是我们之前讨论的修复方案。\n\n我应该简短确认这个状态，然后说接下来怎么办。\n\n但等等，**问题来了**：openclaw.json 里 tts 的 fallbacks 字段是 `[\"minimax(49套餐)/MiniMax-M3\"]`，但 doctor --non-interactive --fix 是 14:35 跑的（在我之前的消息之前），这可能解释了 tts 字段出现的原因 — doctor 自动加了 fallback 链。\n\n而 14:41 跑了 update，14:47 装了 lark 插件。这都是 HALEI 在做事。\n\n所以可能是 HALEI 在我和他对话期间执行了 doctor --fix + update + 装 lark，然后改了 tts 的 fallback。\n\n不管怎样，**配置现在就在那里**。我应该确认 + 简短给个下一步建议。\n\n让我直接回答 HALEI：看到配置了，tts 现在有 3.0 作为 fallback，机制是对的（minimax 抽风就跳到 49套餐的 M3）。要不要现在 trigger 一次 cron 跑跑看验证？或者等下一个调度点（北京时间 22:00 还有一次 21:00 已过的话）。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gcam6zekufd9_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"get","jobId":"5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":298,"output":759,"cacheRead":133845,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134902,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780584788884,"responseId":"0670c45586c12831a273c8d53110b7d9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"75ac8ba1","parentId":"f38b0b09","timestamp":"2026-06-04T14:53:37.173Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gcam6zekufd9_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6\",\n  \"name\": \"TK选品-越泰黑马拦截-v6.0\",\n  \"description\": \"越泰市场趋势黑马拦截策略v6.0：每3小时执行阶段1（白天9-21点），S级爆款触发全流程，直接写入飞书多维表格\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1779088195684,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1780578132145,\n  \"agentId\": \"tts\",\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"0 9,12,15,18,21 * * *\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"执行v6.0选品流程（越泰市场趋势黑马拦截）：\\n1. 调用tiktok_product_trend扫描越南+泰国发饰品类，筛选24小时销量环比≥100%、带货视频≥8个、星级≥4.2、客单价.5-的商品（限30品）\\n2. 发现S级爆款（12小时销量翻倍+视频≥15个+星级≥4.3）立即触发阶段2+3完整验证\\n3. 通过的商品调用ali1688_similar_product核算采购价和毛利率（目标≥40%）\\n4. 将结果写入飞书多维表格AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd/tblHU2do30jzinJT，包含：标题、主图、TikTok销量、Shopee验证数据、1688采购价、毛利率、推荐等级（S/A/B级）\\n5. 发送选品报告到飞书\"\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n    \"accountId\": \"tts\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780621200000,\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780578000011,\n    \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n    \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 132134,\n    \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 6,\n    \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0,\n    \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n    \"lastDiagnostics\": {\n      \"summary\": \"The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.\",\n      \"entries\": [\n        {\n          \"ts\": 1780578132136,\n          \"source\": \"agent-run\",\n          \"severity\": \"error\",\n          \"message\": \"The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"lastDiagnosticSummary\": \"The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.\",\n    \"lastErrorReason\": \"overloaded\",\n    \"lastError\": \"FailoverError: The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.\"\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"id":"5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6","name":"TK选品-越泰黑马拦截-v6.0","description":"越泰市场趋势黑马拦截策略v6.0：每3小时执行阶段1（白天9-21点），S级爆款触发全流程，直接写入飞书多维表格","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1779088195684,"updatedAtMs":1780578132145,"agentId":"tts","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 9,12,15,18,21 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"执行v6.0选品流程（越泰市场趋势黑马拦截）：\n1. 调用tiktok_product_trend扫描越南+泰国发饰品类，筛选24小时销量环比≥100%、带货视频≥8个、星级≥4.2、客单价.5-的商品（限30品）\n2. 发现S级爆款（12小时销量翻倍+视频≥15个+星级≥4.3）立即触发阶段2+3完整验证\n3. 通过的商品调用ali1688_similar_product核算采购价和毛利率（目标≥40%）\n4. 将结果写入飞书多维表格AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd/tblHU2do30jzinJT，包含：标题、主图、TikTok销量、Shopee验证数据、1688采购价、毛利率、推荐等级（S/A/B级）\n5. 发送选品报告到飞书"},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","accountId":"tts"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780621200000,"lastRunAtMs":1780578000011,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":132134,"lastDeliveryStatus":"unknown","consecutiveErrors":6,"consecutiveSkipped":0,"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"unknown","lastDiagnostics":{"summary":"The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.","entries":[{"ts":1780578132136,"source":"agent-run","severity":"error","message":"The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment."}]},"lastDiagnosticSummary":"The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.","lastErrorReason":"overloaded","lastError":"FailoverError: The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment."}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780584817171}}
