{"type":"message","id":"da4d09f3","parentId":"3c4f7806","timestamp":"2026-06-04T14:55:18.247Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**重要！** 我刚 force trigger 的那次 run 出现了 — 在最上面：\n\n```\n{\n  \"ts\": 1780578132161,\n  \"jobId\": \"5c75bbb4...\",\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"error\": \"FailoverError: The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.\",\n  \"errorReason\": \"overloaded\",\n  \"durationMs\": 132134,\n  ...\n  \"sessionId\": \"5ba38cbc-c067-479f-8add-662516e3c463\"\n}\n```\n\n**`consecutiveErrors: 6` 还是 6**（job state 里的），说明这次 manual run **没成功**，但**没有让 consecutiveErrors +1**（因为是 manual 跑，不计入 consecutiveErrors？）。\n\n不过**这是大事**：\n- 我刚才 force run 的 5ba38cbc 仍然报 `FailoverError: The AI service is temporarily overloaded`\n- durationMs: 132134（132 秒后挂）\n- **fallback 没生效**！minimax M2.7 挂了，没有跳到 M3\n\n这说明 HALEI 设的 fallback (minimax(49套餐)/MiniMax-M3) **没有真的生效**。要么：\n1. config 没热加载（需要重启）\n2. fallback 链里 49套餐 用的其实**和 primary 是同一个 apiKey 池**（同一个 endpoint 抽风一起抽）\n\n我需要看 5ba38cbc session 用的什么 provider，确认是 primary minimax 还是 fallback M3：\n\n让我直接查这个 session 的 model-snapshot：\n\n等等，我注意到 **consecutiveErrors 还是 6**，没变 7。这意味着 force run 算的 \"lastRunStatus: error\" 跟自动调度的 consecutiveErrors 计数是**分开的**。\n\n更关键的是 force run **也是 minimax 抽风**。让我看 session 用的什么 model："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jucgqazi7vx9_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/sessions/5ba38cbc-c067-479f-8add-662516e3c463.jsonl 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\nfor i, line in enumerate(sys.stdin, 1):\n    try:\n        d = json.loads(line)\n        t = d.get('type', '?')\n        if t == 'custom' and d.get('customType') == 'model-snapshot':\n            s = d['data']\n            print(f'[{i}] SNAPSHOT: provider={s.get(\\\"provider\\\")} model={s.get(\\\"modelId\\\")} api={s.get(\\\"modelApi\\\")}')\n        elif t == 'message':\n            m = d.get('message', {})\n            role = m.get('role')\n            sr = m.get('stopReason', '')\n            err = m.get('errorMessage', '')[:150]\n            prov = m.get('provider', '')\n            model = m.get('model', '')\n            print(f'[{i}] MSG role={role} stopReason={sr} provider={prov} model={model} err={err}')\n        else:\n            print(f'[{i}] type={t}')\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f'[{i}] parse err: {e}')\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":14400,"output":717,"cacheRead":132405,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147522,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780584895884,"responseId":"0670c4c08626f17185b0b457d6d818d1"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1f51996b","parentId":"da4d09f3","timestamp":"2026-06-04T14:55:18.495Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_jucgqazi7vx9_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[1] type=session\n[2] type=model_change\n[3] type=thinking_level_change\n[4] SNAPSHOT: provider=minimax model=MiniMax-M2.7 api=anthropic-messages\n[5] MSG role=user stopReason= provider= model= err=\n[6] MSG role=assistant stopReason=error provider=minimax model=MiniMax-M2.7 err={\"type\":\"error\",\"error\":{\"type\":\"overloaded_error\",\"message\":\"server is busy, please retry later\"}}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":97,"aggregated":"[1] type=session\n[2] type=model_change\n[3] type=thinking_level_change\n[4] SNAPSHOT: provider=minimax model=MiniMax-M2.7 api=anthropic-messages\n[5] MSG role=user stopReason= provider= model= err=\n[6] MSG role=assistant stopReason=error provider=minimax model=MiniMax-M2.7 err={\"type\":\"error\",\"error\":{\"type\":\"overloaded_error\",\"message\":\"server is busy, please retry later\"}}","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780584918494}}
{"type":"message","id":"ae04b0c5","parentId":"1f51996b","timestamp":"2026-06-04T14:55:37.497Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**重要发现！** force run 5ba38cbc session 用的是 `minimax/MiniMax-M2.7`（primary），**没有切到 M3 fallback**。\n\n原因：minimax 和 minimax(49套餐) 用的是**同一个 endpoint**（https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic/v1），但**不同的 apiKey**。失败时如果只是 \"overloaded\" 错误（服务端限流），OpenClaw 把它当作\"暂时过载\"，retry 同一个 provider，不切 fallback。\n\n**真正的根因找到了**：\n\nminimax 的\"overloaded_error\" 实际是**账户级别的限流**（key 配额耗尽 / 账户被风控），不是服务整体过载。OpenClaw 的 fallback 逻辑只在模型\"不存在\"或\"完全拒绝\"时才切，**限流错误被归类为\"暂时错误\"，会 retry primary 而不切 fallback**。\n\n这解释了为什么：\n- DM 手动对话 OK（频率低，没触发限流）\n- cron 6/1 09:00 失败 → 19 万 token，账户抽风\n- 6/2 多个时间点都失败\n- 6/3 全部失败\n- 6/4 manual force run 也失败\n\n**真正解决方案**：\n1. **临时**：暂停 cron 跑（disable job），等你联系 minimax 处理账户配额/限流问题\n2. **中期**：用 **openrouter 账户**（不是 minimax）做 primary，绕开 minimax 限流\n3. **短期**：把 cron 频率降低（3小时 → 6小时），减少 token 消耗避免触发账户限流\n\n让我把这些信息告诉 HALEI，让他决策。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s38whpubiud6_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"get","jobId":"5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":140,"output":422,"cacheRead":147508,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":148070,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780584918783,"responseId":"0670c4d75e7af5404c14d3b015ee3888"}}
