mary\": \"The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.\",\n    \"lastErrorReason\": \"overloaded\",\n    \"runningAtMs\": 1780584832666\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"id":"5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6","name":"TK选品-越泰黑马拦截-v6.0","description":"越泰市场趋势黑马拦截策略v6.0：每3小时执行阶段1（白天9-21点），S级爆款触发全流程，直接写入飞书多维表格","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1779088195684,"updatedAtMs":1780578132145,"agentId":"tts","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 9,12,15,18,21 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"执行v6.0选品流程（越泰市场趋势黑马拦截）：\n1. 调用tiktok_product_trend扫描越南+泰国发饰品类，筛选24小时销量环比≥100%、带货视频≥8个、星级≥4.2、客单价.5-的商品（限30品）\n2. 发现S级爆款（12小时销量翻倍+视频≥15个+星级≥4.3）立即触发阶段2+3完整验证\n3. 通过的商品调用ali1688_similar_product核算采购价和毛利率（目标≥40%）\n4. 将结果写入飞书多维表格AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd/tblHU2do30jzinJT，包含：标题、主图、TikTok销量、Shopee验证数据、1688采购价、毛利率、推荐等级（S/A/B级）\n5. 发送选品报告到飞书"},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","accountId":"tts"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780621200000,"lastRunAtMs":1780578000011,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":132134,"lastDeliveryStatus":"unknown","consecutiveErrors":6,"consecutiveSkipped":0,"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"unknown","lastDiagnostics":{"summary":"The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.","entries":[{"ts":1780578132136,"source":"agent-run","severity":"error","message":"The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment."}]},"lastDiagnosticSummary":"The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.","lastErrorReason":"overloaded","runningAtMs":1780584832666}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780584937667}}
{"type":"message","id":"cec6c76e","parentId":"0fc3bdd9","timestamp":"2026-06-04T14:55:46.203Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`runningAtMs: 1780584832666` 表示 force run 还在跑（或者已挂掉但 state 没更新）。 `consecutiveErrors: 6` 没动 — 可能 manual 跑不计入 consecutiveErrors 计数。\n\n不过 `lastRunAtMs: 1780578000011` 和 `lastDurationMs: 132134` — 这还是上次 21:00 自动调度失败的数据，force run 没覆盖它（可能 manual 跑不影响自动状态统计）。\n\nOK 我把信息都整理好了，给 HALEI 一个清晰的报告。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nt4demgnp1uj_1","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"kill","sessionId":"lucky-breeze"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":707,"output":156,"cacheRead":148056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":148919,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780584937940,"responseId":"0670c4eaa9f9e1bfcad565862952079c"}}
